to build 
docker compose up --build -d

to view logs for mail verification code 
docker logs final_c-backend-1

to view databae Postgres
docker exec -it final_c-postgres-1 psql -U printuser -d printing_platform

to view all registered users, run this:
docker exec -it final_c-postgres-1 psql -U printuser -d printing_platform -c "SELECT id, username, email, role, is_verified, verification_code FROM users;"

To view your cost estimation materials (like PLA):
docker exec -it final_c-postgres-1 psql -U printuser -d printing_platform -c "SELECT * FROM materials;"

To seed data if calculate cost fails - run seed_data.py
docker exec -it final_c-backend-1 python seed_data.py